tinued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Taillefer was born about 1280, in Cornwall, England, United Kingdom as the son of Richard Taillyfer. He had at least 1 son. He died on 14 October 1366, in England, United Kingdom, at the age of 87."},"et":{"Abt 1280–14 October 1366":"umbes 1280–14. oktoober 1366","1280–1366":"1280–1366","1300–1357":"1300–1357","1260–1336":"1260–1336","14 October 1366":"14. oktoober 1366","1336":"1336","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1366":"1366","1260":"1260","Abt 1280":"umbes 1280","1280":"1280","Kent, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Kent, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Borlase Frank Taillyfer, Cornwall, England":"Cornwall, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1280–14 October 1366":"noin 1280–14. lokakuuta 1366","1280–1366":"1280–1366","1300–1357":"1300–1357","1260–1336":"1260–1336","14 October 1366":"14. lokakuuta 1366","1336":"1336","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1366":"1366","1260":"1260","Abt 1280":"noin 1280","1280":"1280","Kent, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Kent, Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Borlase Frank Taillyfer, Cornwall, England":"Cornwall, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1280–14 October 1366":"environ 1280–14 octobre 1366","1280–1366":"1280–1366","1300–1357":"1300–1357","1260–1336":"1260–1336","14 October 1366":"14 octobre 1366","1336":"1336","1357":"1357","1300":"1300","1366":"1366","1260":"1260","Abt 1280":"environ 1280","1280":"1280","Kent, Kent, England, United Kingdom":"Kent, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Borlase Frank Taillyfer, Cornwall, England":"Cornouailles, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"William Taillefer est né environ 1280, à Cornouailles, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fils de Richard Taillyfer. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé le 14 octobre 1366, à Anglete